data.description:
Welcome to South Beach Party Boats! We’re a team of party people who love creating memorable experiences on our catamaran, boat and yacht excursions. We provide corporate venue sailing and yacht charters for company events, or private occasions such as, birthday or wedding celebrations.  Miami's Leading Party Boat charters for tourist water adventures. Rated a 2018 Trip Advisor Certificate of Excellence for consistent highly rated service.

Our trips depart from docks throughout South Florida. 

Docks include South Beach, Downtown Miami, Hollywood and Fort Lauderdale. 

Trips include the best star island sight-seeing with a variety of options from adult only or all ages and family friendly, and all-inclusive water sports such as: Kayaking, Water Noodles, Masks & Snorkels, Floating Water Mats, Stand-Up Paddle Boarding and Water Trampolines.
